{"tid":1729080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上水太平邨男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T07:31:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7c796bf94d9fb6166e64ab488ba5262a1a1ccc","tid":1729080,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"今早(17日)6時26分，一名男子於上水太平邨平靜樓高處墮下，倒臥地上重創昏迷，驚動保安員報警。救援人員接報到場，當場證實事主已經死亡，以白布覆蓋遺體。警方在場未有檢獲遺書，經調查後證實事主姓毛(39歲)，初步懷疑他由上址走廊墮下，事件沒有可疑，惟事主死因有待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=5ae8b52f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191117/mobile/bkn-20191117074322949-1117_00822_001.html</code></pre>"},{"pid":"b995547386cd82d6a5887098807104d178a12b13","tid":1729080,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:13:25.000Z","msg":"又無可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775c91f3ac037c43bc552d65c2673f0b4ef74f0b","tid":1729080,"uid":182508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:18:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"552e67e017543d3c71f1152904dc8775e4fc96a1","tid":1729080,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f8686dc1b9cc84d6d58f14f931166c775172c01","tid":1729080,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2